/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/12/naukot.png" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – West Virginia University sophomore Joy Naukot is set to compete in the women's 5,000 meters at the NCAA Indoor Track and Field Championships, held March 13-14 at the Randal Tyson Indoor Track in Fayetteville, Ark.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/naukot.png" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/naukot.png"><media:title>Joy Naukot</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/naukot.png" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 14:41:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>16</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58854</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia to Play in Inaugural Riveters Classic</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/12/womens-soccer-west-virginia-to-play-in-inaugural-riveters-classic</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/12/womens-soccer-west-virginia-to-play-in-inaugural-riveters-classic</guid><category>Women's Soccer</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="WSOC26_Riveters Classic_1920x1080" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/12/1920x1080.png" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University women's soccer team will participate in the inaugural Riveters Classic Women's College Showcase, hosted by Pittsburgh Riveters SC on Saturday, April 11, at Highmark Stadium in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/1920x1080.png" /><media:content url="ht